Francois Maltey <fmaltey@nerim.fr> writes:

| No file found, but there is a link :
| 
| ls -l /usr/local/axiom-local/mnt/linux/bin/document
| 
| lrwxrwxrwx 1 root staff 42 2006-10-27 20:43 
